data.description: Charming 3-bedroom, 2 1/2-bathroom home set on 5 acres in Saint George. The spacious living area boasts a cozy fireplace and abundance of natural light, with tall beamed ceilings. The kitchen offers ample cabinetry and counter space, including an eat-in area perfect for quick meals. The dining area is ideal for hosting guests. The main bedroom is generously sized, along with well-proportioned additional bedrooms. Enjoy the converted garage and unwind in the sunroom overlooking the private back yard. The patio is perfect for outdoor dining the can also be enjoyed. The expansive 5-acre yard provides privacy, storage areas, covered parking, and a detached two-car garage. Don't miss this opportunity - book your showing now! Flooring credit will be considered with acceptable offer.
